  <brief_title>Therapeutic Strategy in Advanced Bronchioloalveolar Carcinoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of an Early Therapeutic Permutation on the Tumoral Control of Patients Receiving in First Line a Specific Inhibitor of Tyrosin Kinase of EGFR (Erlotinib) or a Taxan-based Chemotherapy for the Treatment of Not Resecable Adenocarcinoma With Bronchiolo-alveolar.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
