  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate among patients with untreated advanced ADC-CBA, impact on the disease control
      rate after 4 months treatment of an early therapeutic permutation with the first month in the
      absence of stabilization or objective answer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
